.TH "pmcraid_build_ioadl" 9 "pmcraid_build_ioadl" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pmcraid_build_ioadl \- Build a scatter/gather list and map the buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pmcraid_build_ioadl
.BI "(struct pmcraid_instance *pinstance "  ","
.BI "struct pmcraid_cmd *cmd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pinstance" 12
pointer to adapter instance structure
.IP "cmd" 12
pmcraid command struct
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function is invoked by queuecommand entry point while sending a command
to firmware. This builds ioadl descriptors and sets up ioarcb fields.

Return value:
0 on success or -1 on failure
